              "text": "The name of Christ is higher still!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It tells of Him who dwells within us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our old heart to renew and fill."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It tells me of the Spirit’s fullness,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It brings the pow’r of Pentecost."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
